Catalog - Class in gov.usda.DataCatalogClient
The Catalog class is based on Project Open Data metadata specification 1.1 https://project-open-data.cio.gov/v1.1/schema/ and W3C Data Catalog Vocabulary (DCAT) http://www.w3.org/TR/vocab-dcat/ There are a couple of ways to load data into this object.

Catalog.DataListingCode - Enum in gov.usda.DataCatalogClient
The Public Data Listing contains all datasets in datasetList that have accessLevel set for Dataset.AccessLevel.PUBLIC or Dataset.AccessLevel.Restricted.
